name: Start Universal Icons vol.1 Free Sample
description:
Start is a premium handcrafted universal icon set that includes 120 icon in line style

Start includes 120 icons created on a 24 pixels grid and keyline shape. Available SVG, PNG and Figma files and easy to scale and fully customize for your next project.


Key Features

  • 120 Premium Icons
  • Based on 24px grid
  • Keyline Shape
  • Scalable Vector
  • Live Stroke 2px
  • Easy to customize at Figma and other Vector tools
